Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE SECRET SPELL OF FROZEN TIME
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're rather peculiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:02:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But no simple clown could know\Nthe name of that spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't he here just for healing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy, Grand Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This movement...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like he's fighting against a feather!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For anyone who can move like that,{\i0}\N{\i1}being close is actually safer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He fights like straight from{\i0}\N{\i1}a martial arts textbook!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop clinging to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Medoroa... Medoroa... With my Medoroa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, why are you casting\Ntwo Hyado spells?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,there's just a lot of pressure\Non my shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how everything's always\Nended up coming down to Dai or Hyunckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do what I can and end up\Non the ground, which has been fine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,because I've never had everyone count\Non me as the last hope like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just can't move like I usually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! That just proves\Nhow strong you've become!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you not use the power\Nthat you've worked so hard to gain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-Even Grand Master is doing his best!\N-Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A direct hit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,With this well-trained, dried,\Nwithered body of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can float like a leaf in the wind\Nand absorb the force of enemy attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the ultimate skills\Nof my fighting style.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that one hit confirmed my suspicions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body is abnormally cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Over a decade ago, when we fought\NHadorra, the Dark Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra?! How do you know Hadorra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I once fought the Dark Lord long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,with Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, Aban cast a legendary spell\Nfor the first and last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That spell was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the Secret Spell of Frozen Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was 17 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back then, Aban, the Hero traveled with\NRoka, the Warrior and Leira, the Priest,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}on a journey to defeat the Dark Lord.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,ROKA, THE WARRIOR
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Secret Spell of Frozen Time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,ABAN, THE HERO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.02,On Top,,0,0,0,,LEIRA, THE PRIEST
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It freezes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a spell that stops someone's time\Nand holds them in place indefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoever it's cast upon becomes immobile\Nas though Asutoron was cast,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and they become impervious to any force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But unlike Asutoron,\Ntheir biological functions stop, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you've stopped\Ntheir time itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not just a spell\Nto protect oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It can seal an enemy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So you plan to defeat Hadorra,\Nthe Dark Lord with that, Sir Aban?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat him. But I can't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he will be sealed away forever,\Nso peace will be restored to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace to the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've researched this spell using\Nancient tomes so it should work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But today is our only chance to cast it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,During today's once-in-centuries\Ntotal solar eclipse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Once-in-centuries...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Good going, brainy Hero!\NNice find on that spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always held your intellect\Nin high regards! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's get this thing going!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all grasp that\Nonce-in-centuries chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,it won't be all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Roka... Leira...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't drag you two\Ninto this fight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,W-...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I said exactly what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean that this party\Nmust be temporarily disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Aban, why are you saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This secret spell is not fully understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It uses the power of nature\Nso it should work on the Dark Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can hold off\Nthe spell's backlash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In the worst case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'll be caught in the frozen time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we should win peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it's pointless if\Nno one's there to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. Are they fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always fighting. But this time\Nis a little more serious than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't we all work together\Nto fight like we've always done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Like always!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to sacrifice you\Njust to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't allow that, Roka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You really can be so thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to survive to look after\Nthe woman you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:09:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong! I'm not serious\Nor anything about this girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-"This girl"?!\N-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I didn't mean it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you weren't really serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no good.\NYou need to take responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,since you'll be a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Aban, you knew that I'm pregnant\Nwith our child?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't even told Roka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Roka can be quite awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he knew,\Nhe'd still try to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He was always saying "I live by the sword"\Nor "I'll never fall in love with a girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he can be a handful,\Nbut please look after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe a child born in war\Ndeserves to live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do give it a good name, Leira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Matorif!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to risk his life\Nto protect one that will be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's one to talk about awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just as thick as anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a family to mourn me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to make sure Aban doesn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I make it a point not to let women cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go, Brokin.\N-Oof!
