Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Grand Master, for dragging you\Ninto such a perilous fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With my illness,\NI don't have long anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just distract the Dark Lord.\NEven an instant will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a feat only you, the best martial\Nartist in the world, can accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I famous or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Like myself, you're one of the few\Nfamous old geezers in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the riffraff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Strash and Sword Technique{\i0}\N{\i1}are still incomplete.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the only way to obtain peace{\i0}\N{\i1}here and now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bagikurosai!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IORA!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Secret Spell of Frozen Time!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not yet strong enough to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:14:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra and Aban both stood frozen,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}not even blinking an eye.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For a period of over a year,{\i0}\N{\i1}their time remained stopped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so, the Hero brought a brief peace{\i0}\N{\i1}to the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When you came to me seeking training,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly felt the hand of fate at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The child born between Roka and Leira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,was you, Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So the Grand Master{\i0}\N{\i1}was a member of Master Aban's party.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew he was more than he seemed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were an ally of Aban's,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's no mystery that you know\Nthis secret spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But Grand Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't that Secret Spell of Frozen Time\Nsupposed to freeze its target?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's cast on him, then shouldn't\NMystban be immobile?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's utilizing the power of\Nthat Secret Spell for combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how he's doing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but he can still move while the Secret\NSpell of Frozen Time is cast upon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,His very time is frozen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and his body has,\Nas it were, become indestructible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So he takes no damage and is immune\Nto any physical attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like still fighting while under\Nthe effects of a Asutoron spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:16:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're declaring your own death sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can fight while my time is frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...\Nthat I am invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An enemy who could still attack\Nunder the effects of a Asutoron spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}would be unbeatable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to fear, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The spell that Matorif passed down to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On that day,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Matorif could do nothing{\i0}\N{\i1}as he saw Aban sacrifice himself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wracked with guilt, the spell he created{\i0}\N{\i1}for the final battle was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...The Extreme Annihilation Spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Medoroa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a dry leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If grabbed, you can be torn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If dodging is all you can do,\Nthen Larhart would be a more worthy foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Be torn to shreds, clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An instant is all I need!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give me back the strength I once had!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here once again!{\i0}\N{\i1}To save the next generation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh wow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it wasn't Mystban,{\i0}\N{\i1}that first strike would have ended it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never knew Grand Master\Nwas this powerful at full strength!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm burning to go!\NI won't miss this shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They really were all amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All of Master's old friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all here now thanks to\Nthe great people who came before us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't hit this,\NI ain't no Disciple of Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hit him with this Medoroa\Neven if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's already back on his feet. That{\i0}\N{\i1}tenacity is what makes a Disciple of Aban.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with your futile resistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Grand Master!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Warrior Master Style\N{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Earth Wyrm Eruption Strike!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That attack controls the ground!{\i0}\N{\i1}The floor will explode, lifting Mystban!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a dud!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible that spell could defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only last\Nabout a minute at full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Age certainly takes its toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's even shorter\Nthan when I fought Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your miracle plan\Nto turn the tide of battle... is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will you cast your spell\Nand sacrifice him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter, Popp. Cast the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have long to live anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than all of you dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that, Grand Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You disciples of justice\Ncould never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I can now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to let Grand Master\Nand Master enjoy the peace we've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Medoroa!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Rura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He can't dodge that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hit him! Evaporate him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've won!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:17.77,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:28.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:36.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:45.34,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:49.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:56.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:02.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:09.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:15.08,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:20.87,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:27.05,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp and Brokin disappeared in{\i0}\N{\i1}the Medoroa that Mystban reflected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel realizes Mystban's secret,{\i0}\N{\i1}but Kilban appears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.81,0:23:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Aban's defeat becomes apparent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As despair descends upon the heroes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the centuries-old relationship between{\i0}\N{\i1}the two who bear Ban's name is revealed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:23:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Myst and Kill"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:24:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
